1
00:00:19,440 --> 00:00:19,960
What are you doing here?

2
00:00:20,920 --> 00:00:23,199
I saw online this is a popular photo spot. I came to take photos.

3
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:24,719
Photo spot? What photo spot?

4
00:00:24,719 --> 00:00:26,079
This is private property. No entry.

5
00:00:26,679 --> 00:00:27,800
Just a few photos.

6
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:28,320
No.

7
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:29,280
Get lost, get lost!

8
00:00:29,280 --> 00:00:29,679
Okay.

9
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:33,640
Where did that idiot come from?

10
00:00:33,640 --> 00:00:34,159
Tell me about it.

11
00:00:45,759 --> 00:00:46,200
Hey, Da Zhuang.

12
00:00:46,479 --> 00:00:46,960
Hello, Master.

13
00:00:48,079 --> 00:00:49,479
I've been to every herb source.

14
00:00:49,799 --> 00:00:51,159
Only one place is heavily guarded.

15
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:52,039
There's no way to get in.

16
00:00:52,159 --> 00:00:52,560
Where?

17
00:00:53,719 --> 00:00:54,280
Lijia Village.

18
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:57,759
Seems Shen Yue wasn't lying to me.

19
00:00:58,359 --> 00:01:00,520
Yes, Master. Come over and I'll lead the way.

20
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:01,719
No need.

21
00:01:02,679 --> 00:01:04,640
Just go check on Ren Ran at the nursing home for me.

22
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:06,599
I'm quite worried about her.

23
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:09,000
When she's better, bring her back.

24
00:01:09,599 --> 00:01:10,719
Okay, Master.

25
00:01:11,439 --> 00:01:14,120
But she keeps glaring at me with those big eyes. It's creepy.

26
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,879
I bet she still prefers Senior Brother Wu.

27
00:01:18,959 --> 00:01:20,280
She's had it so hard all these years.

28
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,239
Thankfully Senior Brother Wu took care of her.

29
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:25,400
How many days have you even looked after her?

30
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:27,439
Okay.

31
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:33,799
Second Uncle.

32
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,280
My surname may be Shen,

33
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,760
but I'm still a member of the Li Family.

34
00:01:41,079 --> 00:01:42,439
How my mother died back then,

35
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:44,359
you know better than I do.

36
00:01:47,959 --> 00:01:48,719
Feifan.

37
00:01:50,359 --> 00:01:51,239
Why are you here?

38
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,640
Missing me already?

39
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,040
Take me to Lijia Village.

40
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,319
I've checked the USB evidence.

41
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:04,319
The key is in Lijia Village.

42
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,200
Well, since you want my help,

43
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,759
what do I get out of it?

44
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:17,000
You handed me the evidence against the Li Family.

45
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,879
Wasn't it to use me

46
00:02:20,919 --> 00:02:22,400
to help you destroy the Li Family?

47
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:26,319
So if that's the case,

48
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,680
with this favor,

49
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,240
are you going to help me or not?

50
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:35,919
Feifan.

51
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,319
Feifan.

52
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,120
I want to talk to you.

53
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,719
I have nothing to say to you.

54
00:02:52,759 --> 00:02:53,319
Feifan.

55
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,520
Feifan, listen to me.

56
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:57,120
Shen Yue can't be trusted.

57
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:59,400
Last night I saw her meeting with Wang Wenhao.

58
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:00,199
Shen Yue can't be trusted.

59
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,120
And you can be trusted?

60
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:03,680
Don't forget,

61
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:07,120
four years ago, you're the one who put me away.

62
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:32,680
My phone's ringing.

63
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,280
Give me my phone.

64
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:38,639
Come on.

65
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:41,719
No looking at other things when you're with me.

66
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,719
Confiscated. On silent.

67
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:06,599
Ruo Jin, are you with my brother?

68
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:09,120
Ran Ran, it's me.

69
00:04:09,439 --> 00:04:09,879
Brother.

70
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:11,000
Something happened at home.

71
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:11,680
Come back quickly.

72
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:14,280
What?

73
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,199
Where are you going?

74
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:23,560
Ruo Jin, there's an emergency at home.

75
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,199
I need to go home first.

76
00:04:24,759 --> 00:04:25,800
No, you can't go.

77
00:04:26,519 --> 00:04:27,160
You can't go.

78
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,160
If you dare walk out that door today,

79
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:31,279
I'll call the police and say you raped me.

80
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,800
Did you know about this beforehand?

81
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:40,199
Feifan, you can't leave!

82
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:47,399
Mom!

83
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:48,480
Mom!

84
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,360
Mom!

85
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,000
Dad!

86
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:09,480
Dad!

87
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:11,720
Mom!

88
00:05:24,759 --> 00:05:25,360
Ren Feifan.

89
00:05:26,279 --> 00:05:27,600
Someone reported you for rape.

90
00:05:29,079 --> 00:05:29,680
Rape?

91
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,959
Who did I rape?

92
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,560
We are now placing you under arrest

93
00:05:34,079 --> 00:05:36,040
as a suspect in a rape case.

94
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,839
You have the right to remain silent.

95
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:41,279
My parents were murdered!

96
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,439
Aren't you going to do anything?

97
00:05:42,879 --> 00:05:44,399
We'll notify Criminal Division Two immediately.

98
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:46,680
Wait a minute.

99
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,040
Let's go.

100
00:06:15,519 --> 00:06:16,000
Get up.

101
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,120
Move.

102
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:20,680
Feifan.

103
00:06:21,879 --> 00:06:22,399
Calm down.

104
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:23,560
Just calm down.

105
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,439
I'm the one who called the police.

106
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,000
We're a couple.

107
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,439
He didn't rape me.

108
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:30,040
I made the call.

109
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:31,600
I was wrong.

110
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,600
It's my fault.

111
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,800
Don't arrest him.

112
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:34,399
Please, don't take him!

113
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:35,800
You're the one who called?

114
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:36,800
Please, calm down.

115
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:43,879
Now I get it.

116
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,360
This whole thing was a setup.

117
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:57,639
Dad.

118
00:06:58,319 --> 00:06:58,920
Mom.

119
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,000
Rest assured.

120
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:05,279
I won't let a single one of them get away.

121
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:07,480
That's not it, Feifan.

122
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,199
I'm the one who raped her.

123
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:10,839
I'll go with you.

124
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:12,839
Take him away.

125
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,000
What do we do?

126
00:07:19,879 --> 00:07:20,519
What do we do now?

127
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,959
Feifan.

128
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:43,839
Feifan.

129
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,279
Can we...

130
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:49,199
Can we start over, please?

131
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,279
It's too late.

132
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:52,920
Feifan.

133
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,199
Feifan.

134
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:16,199
Feifan.

135
00:08:26,399 --> 00:08:27,319
This time,

136
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,680
I'll be the one protecting you.

137
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,360
Why won't she just go away?

138
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,320
Just ignore her.

139
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,200
Let her follow if she wants.

140
00:08:46,879 --> 00:08:47,240
Over there.

141
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,039
The Young Miss is back.

142
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:03,240
Young Miss, you barely care about family affairs.

143
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,240
What brings you back today?

144
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:08,080
Over the past six months, herbs from other farms

145
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,320
have been shipped on time and in full.

146
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:13,000
Only yours fall short in both quality and quantity.

147
00:09:13,759 --> 00:09:15,360
And you dare ask why I'm here?

148
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:17,799
Um...

149
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:20,639
These two seem unfamiliar.

150
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:21,519
I haven't seen them around.

151
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:22,600
Who are they?

152
00:09:22,799 --> 00:09:23,879
They're from the city Drug Administration.

153
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,840
They found problems with our herbs.

154
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:30,120
Luckily, we're personal friends.

155
00:09:30,879 --> 00:09:32,879
So they came as friends to take a look.

156
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:36,320
Village Chief Li, if the herbs really have issues

157
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,960
and this gets escalated to the Drug Bureau,

158
00:09:39,759 --> 00:09:42,600
you won't be able to handle the fallout.

159
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:44,600
Right, right, of course.

160
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:46,559
How about this:

161
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:51,919
Let me show the Young Miss and the two officials around.

162
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,039
If you don't mind,

163
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:54,840
try some of our country cooking.

164
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,159
Stay the night here.

165
00:09:56,799 --> 00:09:59,200
Tomorrow, I'll report to you both

166
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,279
in detail about Lijia Village's situation.

167
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:13,039
Ginseng, matsutake.

168
00:10:16,039 --> 00:10:18,559
When you bring them their meals later,

169
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:19,600
keep a close eye on them.

170
00:10:21,039 --> 00:10:22,000
And don't eat any of it.

171
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:23,720
There's a drug in the food.

172
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,120
It's not poison.

173
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:28,360
I just want them to sleep soundly.

174
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:29,639
Don't cause me any trouble.

175
00:10:30,759 --> 00:10:32,159
The stuff in the warehouse is fine, right?

176
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:34,399
No problem.

177
00:10:35,919 --> 00:10:36,440
Good then.

178
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:00,879
Young Miss.

179
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,720
The Village Chief said you can't wander around.

180
00:11:04,399 --> 00:11:05,559
There's a problem with the herbs.

181
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,440
Of course we have to check the fields.

182
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:08,399
Move aside.

183
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:12,360
Young Miss, the mountain is full of snakes and bugs.

184
00:11:12,559 --> 00:11:13,519
Especially venomous snakes.

185
00:11:14,039 --> 00:11:15,799
You should just have a good meal today.

186
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:16,759
And get some proper rest.

187
00:11:17,279 --> 00:11:18,639
The Village Chief will arrange everything tomorrow.

188
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:28,279
To welcome the Young Miss and the two officials,

189
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,360
the Village Chief

190
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:31,360
brought out all his finest ingredients.

191
00:11:32,399 --> 00:11:34,320
Please, help yourselves.

192
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,000
Tastes pretty good.

193
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:17,639
Okay.

194
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,159
I got it, Boss Li.

195
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:21,840
Alright.

196
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:22,519
Don't worry.

197
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:25,480
I'll send the Young Miss back first thing tomorrow.

198
00:12:26,519 --> 00:12:27,360
Okay, okay, hanging up now.

199
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:29,799
Why does it reek so bad in here?

200
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:32,279
Bury all these corpses tonight!

201
00:12:59,159 --> 00:13:00,519
I didn't eat that much.

202
00:13:02,399 --> 00:13:03,600
I knew they drugged the food.

203
00:13:04,159 --> 00:13:05,279
But it wasn't poison.

204
00:13:07,759 --> 00:13:10,360
Are you sure you want to keep talking to me like this?

205
00:13:16,919 --> 00:13:18,240
Let's go check on Shen Yue.

206
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,000
What's going on?

207
00:13:32,519 --> 00:13:32,960
She's fine.

208
00:13:33,919 --> 00:13:35,799
She just ate too much, so the dose was too high.

209
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,200
She'll wake up soon.

210
00:13:38,759 --> 00:13:40,519
Then why didn't you tell us?

211
00:13:41,919 --> 00:13:43,360
The skilled are bold.

212
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,519
This drug just makes us sleep more deeply.

213
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:49,639
Probably afraid we'd wander around at night.

214
00:13:50,919 --> 00:13:52,879
Since we ate it without suspicion,

215
00:13:52,879 --> 00:13:55,200
they won't be on guard against us.

216
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:58,440
I've noticed you're getting craftier and craftier.

217
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:01,799
You're a bit different from before.

218
00:14:03,399 --> 00:14:06,279
Are you saying I used to be dumb?

